summary: A toxic green coloration of the Daedric armor set.
descriptionHtml:
A toxic green variation of the Daedric armor set with lots of a little highlights and green, glowing eyes.

Mod Manager friendly.

Daedric changes both male and female, no avoiding it.

If you like it, say somethin\' so I\'ll know to keep doing more!
